methods.void add(int index, E element): Inserts the specified element at the specified position in this list (optional operation).
methods.boolean addAll(int index, Collection c): Inserts all of the elements in the specified collection into this list at the specified position (optional operation).
methods.E get(int index): Returns the element at the specified position in this list.
methods.Iterator iterator(): Returns an iterator over the elements in this list (in proper sequence).
methods.ListIterator listIterator(int index): Returns a list iterator over the elements in this list (in proper sequence).
methods.E remove(int index): Removes the element at the specified position in this list (optional operation).
methods.E set(int index, E element): Replaces the element at the specified position in this list with the specified element (optional operation).
